data.title: Neighborhood Navigator
data.meta_description: Connect your patients with resources in their neighborhoods by using our Neighborhood Navigator tool.
data.text:
The EveryONE Project offers you screening tools to identify patientsâ€™ social needs and address health equity in your practice. The Neighborhood Navigator is the next step for you to improve social determinants of health among your patients.

Use this interactive tool at the point of care to connect patients with supportive resources in their neighborhoods. It lists more than 40,000 social services by zip code.
